OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FSpanish authorities are preparing to
OL,7,Freceive more than 140 passengers and
OL,8,Fcrew members aboard the hantavirus-
OL,9,Fstricken cruise ship MV Hondius, which
OL,10,Fis heading for the Canary Islands.
OL,12,FLocal health officials say they will
OL,13,Fcarry out careful evacuations when the
OL,14,Fcruise ship docks at Tenerife on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,17,FSo far, three people have died
OL,18,Ffollowing the outbreak, and multiple
OL,19,Fothers have been diagnosed with
OL,20,Fsuspected hantavirus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
