OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FBut what will evacuation procedures
OL,7,Flook like and how will Spain ensure
OL,8,Fpassengers on the MV Hondius do not
OL,9,Fcome into contact with local residents?
OL,11,FITV News explains.
OL,13,FHow will MV Hondius passengers be
OL,14,Fevacuated?
OL,16,FSpanish officials have laid out their
OL,17,Fplans for what to do with passengers
OL,18,Fand crew once the MV Hondius is docked
OL,19,Fin Tenerife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
