OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FThe ship will not get close to the
OL,7,Fport when it arrives, they said.
OL,8,FInstead, a team of medics will go out
OL,9,Fon small boats to examine passengers
OL,10,Fand crew before moving them in groups
OL,11,Fof five.
OL,13,FOnce on land, the group will be
OL,14,Fisolated and immediately put into cars
OL,15,Fthat will head straight to the runway
OL,16,Fof the airport, where individual
OL,17,Fcountries have sent their own planes.
OL,19,FThe journey to the airport will take
OL,20,Fapproximately 10 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FPeople will not be allowed to leave
OL,7,Fthe ship until their flight
OL,8,Farrangements have been confirmed.
OL,10,FThis process will be supervised by the
OL,11,FSpanish government at all times.
OL,13,FWhich countries are sending planes to
OL,14,Fcollect their citizens?
OL,16,FThe US has agreed to send a plane to
OL,17,Frepatriate its 17 citizens on board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
