OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FThe British government has also said
OL,7,Fit will charter a flight to evacuate
OL,8,Fthe nearly two dozen British
OL,9,Fnationals, who will be asked to self-
OL,10,Fisolate for 45 days when they return.
OL,12,FHow are Tenerife locals responding to
OL,13,Fthe vessel's arrival?
OL,15,FDespite Spanish authorities' attempts
OL,16,Fto reassure residents that passengers
OL,17,Fwill be contained and kept away from
OL,18,Fthe public, fears remain among locals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
