OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FSome Tenerife residents have joined a
OL,7,Fprotest outside the Canary Islands
OL,8,FParliament, demanding strict safety
OL,9,Fmeasures ahead of the ship's expected
OL,10,Farrival on Sunday.
OL,12,FSome have not ruled out trying to
OL,13,Fprevent the ship from docking, though
OL,14,Fthey have not said how they would do
OL,15,Fso.
OL,17,FThe protesters are calling for clear
OL,18,Fsafety protocols, including the use of
OL,19,Ftugboats and protective equipment,
OL,20,Funder the slogan "Respect Tenerife.
OL,21,FSafety Protocols".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
