OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FWhat is the risk to the public?
OL,8,FGiven the long incubation period,
OL,9,Fthere could be more cases among crew,
OL,10,Fpassengers, and contacts of those
OL,11,Falready infected.
OL,13,FBut the UK Health Security Agency and
OL,14,Fthe World Health Organisation have
OL,15,Fstressed the risk to the wider public
OL,16,Fis low.
OL,18,F"This is not Covid, this is not
OL,19,Finfluenza, it spreads very, very
OL,20,Fdifferently," WHO's Maria Van Kerkhove
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
