OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FWhere are those with the virus?
OL,8,FA Dutch man who died on board was
OL,9,Ftaken off the ship at St Helena, but
OL,10,Fwas not tested for the virus. His wife
OL,11,Flater fell ill on a flight to
OL,12,FJohannesburg and died upon arrival at
OL,13,Fthe hospital.
OL,15,FTests confirmed she had hantavirus.
OL,16,FAuthorities are now tracing people she
OL,17,Fcame into contact with en route.
OL,19,FThe body of a German woman who died
OL,20,Fremains on board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
