OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FA man who went to the ship's doctor
OL,7,Fwith symptoms was evacuated from
OL,8,FAscension Island to South Africa,
OL,9,Fwhere he is in intensive care but
OL,10,Fbelieved to be improving. He also
OL,11,Ftested positive.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
