OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778284974
OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FAnother passenger who disembarked at
OL,7,FSt Helena returned to Switzerland but
OL,8,Fsought medical care in Zurich after
OL,9,Fdeveloping symptoms. He has since been
OL,10,Fadmitted to the hospital and tested
OL,11,Fpositive.
OL,13,FThree further cases were evacuated to
OL,14,Fthe Netherlands for treatment, among
OL,15,Fthem a Dutch crew member, a German
OL,16,Fwoman who flew to Dusseldorf, and
OL,17,FMartin Anstee, a 56-year-old retired
OL,18,FBritish police officer who worked on
OL,19,Fthe ship as an expedition guide and is
OL,20,Fnow in hospital in Leiden.
OL,26,@xD@Txz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
