OL,3,CInside the evacuation plans for the
OL,4,Chantavirus-hit cruise ship
OL,6,FA woman in Amsterdam, reported to be a
OL,7,Fflight attendant who came into contact
OL,8,Fwith the Dutch woman who died in South
OL,9,FAfrica, came forward with potential
OL,10,Fsymptoms on Thursday.
OL,12,FTwo Brits who left the ship at St
OL,13,FHelena in late April have returned to
OL,14,Fthe UK and are self-isolating, though
OL,15,Fneither has reported symptoms. Close
OL,16,Fcontacts of those on board are also
OL,17,Fself-isolating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
